Name
       lefDefOutVersion

Syntax
        lefDefOutVersion <version_num>

       Type: String

       Default: 5.8

       Specifies  LEF/DEF output version. Possible string values are 5.5, 5.6,
       5.7, 5.8, and 6.0. The default is 5.8.

